data.description: No need to wait for a new build! This townhome is move-in ready, pristine condition with a finished basement! Radiating with natural light, this Central Park townhome is poised in a prime location. A front porch w/ a swing overlooks serene views of a green space and trail. Further inside, an open and airy layout unfolds w/ a soothing color palette. A spacious living and dining area presents ample room for entertaining guests. Grounded by a center island w/ seating, a bright kitchen boasts all-white cabinetry, a chic tiled backsplash and a pantry. From the kitchen, step outside to enjoy a shaded outdoor entertaining and sitting area and access to the two car garage. A sunlit primary suite features a sizable walk-in closet and a five-piece bath w/ a large bathtub. The upper level is complete w/ two additional bedrooms, one of which features a walk-in closet, an additional full bath, and a laundry area. Downstairs, a rare finished basement offers flexible living space and ample storage w/ a living room/flex area, currently being used as a home gym, full bedroom, full bath with gorgeous designer tile finishes, non-conforming flex/office space with closet, and a large utility room with storage space. This coveted location affords proximity to desirable amenities including Splash Landing Pool, Dick’s Sporting Goods Park, Rocky Mountain Arsenal National Wildlife Refuge, The Shops at Beeler Park, Central Park nature trails and, coming early summer 2024, the Pearl Market, a daily gathering place where you can get a cup of coffee or shop for your daily grocery needs. Pearl Market will feature a full butcher and seafood counter, fresh housemade pasta, fresh produce, locally sourced eggs, and all the ingredients for your daily meals. See https://www.thepearlcollectiveco.com/ for more details.
